{"TopicId":192834,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Screenshot","CreatedByName":"Space Nerd","CreatedById":198691,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-01T12:33:48Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Space Nerd","CreatedById":198691,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-01T12:33:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo Alt\u002Bf1 to\u00A0screenshot works when the game is still loading?(probably not)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf not, is there a way to screenshot the loading screen?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-01T13:01:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlt-Prnt Screen on Windows. Then paste that from the clipboard into some bitmap editor like Paint.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RoninFrog","CreatedById":203049,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-01T18:21:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nshift\u002Bcommand\u002B3 on mac.\u00A0 Should save to desktop.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBe careful though, as shift controls the throttle.\u00A0 You could end up getting a nice picture of\u00A0an ugly wreck.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MichaelMoore","CreatedById":203881,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-09T13:19:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust get the prntscreet app. It works mostly everywhere\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-04-09T13:19:24Z\u0022 title=\u002204/09/2020 01:19  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EApril 9, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by MichaelMoore\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stamp20","CreatedById":202020,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-09T17:25:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nF12 takes screenshots on Steam.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Chequers","CreatedById":202186,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-04-10T08:33:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223768512\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022192834\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221586453128\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022202020\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Stamp20\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n15 hours ago, Stamp20 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nF12 takes screenshots on Steam.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd also, by default, turns on the aerodynamic forces overlay - so you might want to rebind it.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}